{"tid":799228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理財「應使則使」　劉鳴煒：10歲生日收10萬現金，全部存銀行","createTime":"2018-08-30T01:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T01:52:46.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0620133a635a2a0c06acaa1e56dba21b110dec","tid":799228,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=f2d740fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&h=6f060fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚播出的港台電視節目《講錢。講呢啲》，邀請青年發展委員會副主席、華人置業主席劉鳴煒訪問。主持任美貞問，當一個人金錢多得花不完，理財目的何在？劉鳴煒說，理財可以是個人紀律的延伸，沒有人希望身家「少咗幾個零」：「當你有細路仔、有屋企人、有想照顧的人，自然會想慢慢增值。」<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒在節目中提到，家庭教育教曉自己「應使則使，應慳則慳」。他記得10歲生日當天，父母給他10萬元現金，他此後半年一元也沒花過，只是天天或隔日在數鈔票，最後存進與母親開設的聯名戶口。他說，當年不懂投資，但至少知道不應該亂花錢。<br />\n<br />\n他強調不喜歡炒炒賣賣，投資計劃短則3年，長的可達7年、10年。他又分享自己「輸得最慘一次」，是2000年左右未及脫離科網泡沫，在歐美市場損手，雖然沒有變「牆紙」，事後會反省為何察覺不到：「金融史是有教育意義的，人性會不斷重覆。」"},{"pid":"85bd09f2785ba6b0adf7fd503160cf5b413a79a1","tid":799228,"uid":199145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚勵志啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ad5657e7e41470fecf5323b48502d2d30f6450","tid":799228,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ese